 EDITOR'S NOTE: <PERSON> Isaac </PERSON> <PERSON> A. </PERSON> <PERSON> Levi </PERSON> has been covering Latin American for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> for 25 years, the last 14 of them based in <LOCATION> Mexico </LOCATION> <LOCATION> City </LOCATION>.
