<DATELINE>JOHANNESBURG, South Africa (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 Police used mine detectors Saturday to check cars arriving at a <LOCATION> Pretoria </LOCATION> rugby stadium as part of tightened security measures following a series of bombings. A mine attached to a telephone pole exploded outside the clubhouse of a field hockey team in a <LOCATION> Johannesburg </LOCATION> suburb. No serious injuries were reported. At a rugby match in <LOCATION> Cape </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Town </LOCATION>, a police helicopter circled the stadium. Last weekend, a car bomb exploded outside a <LOCATION> Johannesburg </LOCATION> stadium as spectators left a rugby match. Two people died and 35 were injured. Other recent targets included a video game arcade and a beachfront restaurant. On Saturday, a large police contingent was on duty at <LOCATION> Pretoria </LOCATION>'s main rugby stadium Spectators arriving for the game were searched as they entered the grounds, and mine detectors were used to scan underneath vehicles entering parking lots. Police have blamed the recent bombings on the outlawed <ORGANIZATION> African </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> National </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Congress </ORGANIZATION> guerrilla movement, which has neither claimed nor denied responsibility. The <ORGANIZATION> ANC </ORGANIZATION> is the main group fighting to overthrow <LOCATION> South </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Africa </LOCATION>'s government. Authorities across the country have launched a `` bomb awareness campaign'' to encourage greater public vigilance. City officials in <LOCATION> Johannesburg </LOCATION> are publicizing a special emergency telephone number to be used for reporting suspected bombs, and the <ORGANIZATION> Cape </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Town </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Chamber </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Commerce </ORGANIZATION> has published a set of security guidelines to shopowners. Even before the bombings intensified over the past four months, posters were on display in many government buil