 </LOCATION>, said she had operated the farm as a non-profit organization for five years, mostly to raise and train animals and take them to schools to teach children about wildlife. She said she would now close the farm. It was animals from Animal Advocates that starred in the movie `` <PERSON> Harry </PERSON> and the <ORGANIZATION> Hendersons </ORGANIZATION>,'' Ms. <PERSON> Gordon </PERSON> said.
