<HEAD>Dukakis Says Bush Plan To Boost Fees Is Tax Increase</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: INSERTS 3 grafs after 2nd graf pvs, bgng: ``I understand
...'' to UPDATE with Jackson comments; SUBS 20th graf, bgng:
``Dukakis was ...'' to delete first reference to Jackson.</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By WILLIAM M. WELCH</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
